26#pragma once
27
28#include "CacheStorageEngineCache.h"
29#include "NetworkCacheStorage.h"
30#include <WebCore/ClientOrigin.h>
31#include <wtf/CompletionHandler.h>
32#include <wtf/Deque.h>
33
34namespace WebCore {
35class StorageQuotaManager;
36}
37
38namespace WebKit {
39
40namespace CacheStorage {
41
42class Engine;
43
44class Caches final : public RefCounted<Caches> {
45public:
46 static String cachesSizeFilename(const String& cachesRootsPath);
47 static Ref<Caches> create(Engine&, WebCore::ClientOrigin&&, String&& rootPath);
48 ~Caches();
49
50 static void retrieveOriginFromDirectory(const String& folderPath, WorkQueue&, WTF::CompletionHandler<void(std::optional<WebCore::ClientOrigin>&&)>&&);
51
52 void initialize(WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CompletionCallback&&);
53 void open(const String& name, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CacheIdentifierCallback&&);
54 void remove(uint64_t identifier, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CacheIdentifierCallback&&);
55 void dispose(Cache&);
56
57 void detach();
58
59 bool isInitialized() const { return m_isInitialized; }
60 void cacheInfos(uint64_t updateCounter, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CacheInfosCallback&&);
61
62 Cache* find(uint64_t identifier);
63 void appendRepresentation(StringBuilder&) const;
64
65 void readRecordsList(Cache&, NetworkCache::Storage::TraverseHandler&&);
66 void readRecord(const NetworkCache::Key&, WTF::Function<void(Expected<WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::Record, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::Error>&&)>&&);
67
68 void requestSpace(uint64_t spaceRequired, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CompletionCallback&&);
69 void writeRecord(const Cache&, const RecordInformation&, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::Record&&, uint64_t previousRecordSize, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CompletionCallback&&);
70
71 void removeCacheEntry(const NetworkCache::Key&);
72 void removeRecord(const RecordInformation&);
73
74 const NetworkCache::Salt& salt() const;
75 const WebCore::ClientOrigin& origin() const { return m_origin; }
76
77 bool shouldPersist() const { return !m_rootPath.isNull(); }
78
79 void clear(WTF::CompletionHandler<void()>&&);
80 void clearMemoryRepresentation();
81
82 uint64_t storageSize() const;
83 void updateSizeFile(CompletionHandler<void()>&&);
84
85private:
86 Caches(Engine&, WebCore::ClientOrigin&&, String&& rootPath);
87
88 void initializeSize();
89 void readCachesFromDisk(WTF::Function<void(Expected<Vector<Cache>, WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::Error>&&)>&&);
90 void writeCachesToDisk(WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CompletionCallback&&);
91
92 void storeOrigin(WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CompletionCallback&&);
93 static std::optional<WebCore::ClientOrigin> readOrigin(const NetworkCache::Data&);
94
95 Cache* find(const String& name);
96 void clearPendingWritingCachesToDiskCallbacks();
97
98 void makeDirty() { ++m_updateCounter; }
99 bool isDirty(uint64_t updateCounter) const;
100
101 bool hasActiveCache() const;
102
103 bool m_isInitialized { false };
104 Engine* m_engine { nullptr };
105 uint64_t m_updateCounter { 0 };
106 WebCore::ClientOrigin m_origin;
107 String m_rootPath;
108 uint64_t m_size { 0 };
109 Vector<Cache> m_caches;
110 Vector<Cache> m_removedCaches;
111 RefPtr<NetworkCache::Storage> m_storage;
112 HashMap<NetworkCache::Key, std::unique_ptr<WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::Record>> m_volatileStorage;
113 mutable std::optional<NetworkCache::Salt> m_volatileSalt;
114 Vector<WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::CompletionCallback> m_pendingInitializationCallbacks;
115 bool m_isWritingCachesToDisk { false };
116 Deque<CompletionHandler<void(std::optional<WebCore::DOMCacheEngine::Error>)>> m_pendingWritingCachesToDiskCallbacks;
117};
118
119} // namespace CacheStorage
120
121} // namespace WebKit
